title: Phoenix from Another World
overview: This ancient romance, which combines elements of time travel, medicine, love, and palace struggle, tells the story of a modern female special forces soldier who accidentally travels to ancient times and becomes a medical fairy with peerless medical skills. Not only does she have extraordinary talent in medical skills, but she also uses her unique personality and wisdom to navigate the complex palace life with ease. In ancient times, she met a handsome and powerful prince, and a complex, love-hate relationship unfolded between the two. The prince was originally cold and ruthless, but the appearance of the medical fairy gradually changed him, allowing him to experience the warmth of love and the brilliance of human nature. However, the power struggles in the palace and the misunderstandings between them made their love journey full of twists and turns and challenges.
